Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:21.46,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胆小爱哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:27.00,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}又想吻你的我
