Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:38.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却总是犹犹豫豫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:41.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}常常后悔着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:49.03,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅仅是伙伴 不能成为爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.18,0:01:53.58,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想守护 却无法在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:57.03,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在矛盾中苦恼
